\f1\b \cb2 Week 1 (Jan 8)\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0
\f0\b0 \cb1 \

\f1\b \cb2 Lecture/Discussion:
\f0\b0 \'a0
\f2\i Course introduction. Understanding client problems & needs, forming client relationships, managing client meetings.\'a0
\f0\i0 \cb1 \

\f1\b \cb2 Task 1:
\f0\b0 \'a0Mark initial project preference on Canvas Assignment document for Task 1.\cb1 \

\f1\b \cb2 Reading:
